&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>From our experience we say&lt;br>
Doing transaction of any kind &lt;br>
Whether social, commercial, religious &lt;br>
We need another &lt;br>
But if we don&amp;rsquo;t know about another &lt;br>
Then transaction can be risky &lt;br>
It can cause pain, hurt, loss or suffering &lt;br>
Therefore don&amp;rsquo;t transact with unknown. &lt;br>
(a frequently used proverb)&lt;/p>
&lt;p>But, how do we know someone without transacting?&lt;br>
After transaction only we know &lt;br>
Transaction with unknown person maybe good or bad.&lt;br>
But the same applies to your known &lt;br>
If you know someone and then transact &lt;br>
In that case also transaction maybe good or bad.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>